WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.819
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.820 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.695
=Episode 12=

00:01:26.740 --> 00:01:28.579
It may sting a little. Bear with it.

00:01:32.162 --> 00:01:34.286
笙ｪNight rain falls before the courtyard笙ｪ

00:01:34.287 --> 00:01:37.698
笙ｪIlluminating the partings
of the mortal world笙ｪ

00:01:37.699 --> 00:01:38.819
Does it hurt?

00:01:39.180 --> 00:01:40.459
If it does,

00:01:41.979 --> 00:01:43.099
hold on to me.

00:01:46.317 --> 00:01:49.556
笙ｪA sharp arrow pierces through memory笙ｪ

00:01:49.557 --> 00:01:53.261
笙ｪLonging spreads like ink笙ｪ

00:01:53.262 --> 00:02:00.586
笙ｪBeaded curtains divide love
and hate at either end笙ｪ

00:02:00.587 --> 00:02:06.682
笙ｪAfter endless sorrow endured,
love is a word too hard to sever笙ｪ

00:02:07.537 --> 00:02:14.024
笙ｪPast ties fade like a dream gone cold,
in giving all, we found our only joy笙ｪ

00:02:14.025 --> 00:02:17.519
笙ｪThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms笙ｪ

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:21.239
笙ｪOne night of snow
fell wild and restless笙ｪ

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:25.338
笙ｪEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regret笙ｪ

00:02:25.339 --> 00:02:28.511
It seems it does not hurt as much now.

00:02:28.512 --> 00:02:31.759
笙ｪWith blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell笙ｪ

00:02:31.760 --> 00:02:35.759
笙ｪNo more longing will enter my dreams笙ｪ

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:42.382
笙ｪWhen all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with you笙ｪ

00:03:16.460 --> 00:03:19.300
Thunder frightens me.

00:04:04.700 --> 00:04:07.232
(The Gu Family Chronicle)

00:04:07.900 --> 00:04:08.819
Official,

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:10.819
Miss Song has indeed taken action.

00:04:11.740 --> 00:04:12.900
(Song Zhiyun,)

00:04:13.059 --> 00:04:14.740
(why are you looking into)

00:04:15.059 --> 00:04:16.659
(the Gu family records?)

00:04:38.779 --> 00:04:41.140
You are back
rather early today, Official Gu.

00:04:41.179 --> 00:04:42.499
Are your duties finished?

00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:46.380
I heard there was
a rat stirring trouble at home,

00:04:46.659 --> 00:04:48.260
so I returned to take a look.

00:04:48.859 --> 00:04:50.260
As for you,

00:04:51.900 --> 00:04:53.419
why are you here,

00:04:54.339 --> 00:04:56.020
and what are you doing?

00:04:58.179 --> 00:05:00.900
I am not doing anything.

00:05:02.659 --> 00:05:04.099
What is that

00:05:06.187 --> 00:05:07.780
in your hand?

00:05:09.900 --> 00:05:11.099
This...

00:05:12.140 --> 00:05:13.780
Actually, I...

00:05:24.700 --> 00:05:27.579
(With reverence to the Star Lord
of Matchmaking, who governs mortal marriages.)

00:05:27.580 --> 00:05:31.080
(I, Song Zhiyun, born in the Year of Yihai,
second month, twelfth day, at midnight,)

00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:33.418
(harbor deep affection for Gu Chengye,
born in the Year of Yichou,)

00:05:33.419 --> 00:05:36.098
(on the thirteenth day of the eighth month,
at the hour of Chen. Our bond runs deep.)

00:05:36.099 --> 00:05:39.359
(May the Star Lord of Matchmaking bless us
that Gu Chengye and I be joined in marriage,)

00:05:39.359 --> 00:05:41.220
(and live in happiness.
I bow in reverence.)

00:05:41.739 --> 00:05:42.979
You...

00:05:43.140 --> 00:05:45.340
I have liked you for a long time.

00:05:47.060 --> 00:05:49.099
(So when she took the family chronicle,)

00:05:49.140 --> 00:05:50.859
(it was only to learn my birth details.)

00:05:52.339 --> 00:05:53.978
If you feel

00:05:53.979 --> 00:05:55.379
I am not worthy of you,

00:05:55.380 --> 00:05:57.099
that I am overreaching,

00:05:58.539 --> 00:05:59.659
then this...

00:06:00.580 --> 00:06:02.260
Just pretend you never saw it.

00:06:04.580 --> 00:06:06.539
(I have gone this far with the act,)

00:06:06.739 --> 00:06:08.299
(and he still has no reaction.)

00:06:08.412 --> 00:06:10.172
(I will press a little further.)

00:06:11.739 --> 00:06:13.739
I know this is improper,

00:06:14.099 --> 00:06:15.780
but I cannot help my feelings.

00:06:17.099 --> 00:06:19.020
If it displeases you,

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.178
I will leave the Gu Residence.

00:06:21.179 --> 00:06:22.499
Wait.

00:06:25.739 --> 00:06:27.380
I told you that day

00:06:27.659 --> 00:06:29.179
I would keep you safe.

00:06:29.739 --> 00:06:30.859
You...

00:06:32.460 --> 00:06:34.380
You stay at the Gu Residence in peace.

00:06:35.460 --> 00:06:36.979
Thank you, Official Gu.

00:06:39.539 --> 00:06:41.020
(She)

00:06:41.539 --> 00:06:43.499
(has feelings for me.)

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:49.932
(Gu Residence)

00:06:52.339 --> 00:06:55.580
(She truly has feelings for me.)

00:06:59.779 --> 00:07:00.859
You unfilial son.

00:07:01.060 --> 00:07:02.539
Come out at once.

00:07:04.859 --> 00:07:05.979
(Could it be)

00:07:06.179 --> 00:07:07.699
(that the Duke discovered)

00:07:07.700 --> 00:07:09.340
(Lady Gu founded the Shengtang Guild?)

00:07:09.539 --> 00:07:10.699
(Disgracing the family name,)

00:07:10.700 --> 00:07:13.380
(her spirit tablet removed,
banned forever from the ancestral hall?)

00:07:13.539 --> 00:07:15.380
(That is no small charge.)

00:07:16.539 --> 00:07:17.538
Gu Chengye,

00:07:17.539 --> 00:07:19.900
you have gone too far.

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:25.262
Outrageous, truly outrageous.

00:07:25.659 --> 00:07:26.978
You are the heir to a ducal house,

00:07:26.979 --> 00:07:29.178
and yet you bring a courtesan
into your home.

00:07:29.179 --> 00:07:31.460
Where is the dignity
of the Duke's household?

00:07:32.539 --> 00:07:33.418
Guards.

00:07:33.419 --> 00:07:35.699
(The Duke of Yu, Gu Chengye's father)
Bring that woman to me at once.

00:07:35.700 --> 00:07:36.499
Yes, master.

00:07:36.500 --> 00:07:38.099
If Father insists on searching,

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.699
then I will give up
my path to advancement.

00:07:40.700 --> 00:07:42.098
As for the future of the Gu family,

00:07:42.099 --> 00:07:43.659
let whoever wishes to bear it do so.

00:07:46.412 --> 00:07:48.311
You are the young heir,

00:07:48.312 --> 00:07:50.260
yet for the sake of a woman like that,

00:07:50.659 --> 00:07:52.900
you would disregard
the honor of this house.

00:07:53.460 --> 00:07:54.538
Our Gu family

00:07:54.539 --> 00:07:56.380
cannot bear another stain.

00:07:57.739 --> 00:07:59.020
A stain?

00:08:00.299 --> 00:08:02.539
Are you speaking of my mother?

00:08:03.700 --> 00:08:05.260
How absurd.

00:08:05.337 --> 00:08:08.099
She was virtuous and devoted to you.

00:08:08.419 --> 00:08:09.899
Yet in the end she is judged this way.

00:08:09.900 --> 00:08:11.019
Enough.

00:08:11.020 --> 00:08:12.658
Why do you avoid the truth?

00:08:12.659 --> 00:08:13.900
All these years,

00:08:14.219 --> 00:08:15.658
you only sought to bury the scandal.

00:08:15.659 --> 00:08:17.859
Have you ever tried
to uncover what truly happened?

00:08:18.299 --> 00:08:21.499
What happened so many years ago,
was it her name that was tainted,

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:23.020
or was it your conscience?

00:08:24.299 --> 00:08:25.619
Insolence.

00:08:29.060 --> 00:08:30.619
I am no longer a child.

00:08:31.539 --> 00:08:33.578
And I will not repeat the same mistake.

00:08:33.579 --> 00:08:35.739
I gave my word that I would protect her.

00:08:35.740 --> 00:08:37.340
In this life,

00:08:37.939 --> 00:08:39.499
I will never betray her.

00:08:40.500 --> 00:08:43.070
Very well. So you claim you
will not break your word.

00:08:43.140 --> 00:08:44.499
Then kneel here.

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.259
Kneel until you come to your senses.

00:08:46.740 --> 00:08:48.632
I want to see

00:08:48.819 --> 00:08:50.139
just how deep your devotion runs.

00:08:57.620 --> 00:08:58.420
Wei Cheng,

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:00.180
what is going on?

00:09:00.220 --> 00:09:01.859
Miss Song, please reconsider.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.859
Official Gu went
to great lengths to protect you.

00:09:03.860 --> 00:09:05.139
If you act rashly now

00:09:05.140 --> 00:09:06.379
and anger the Duke,

00:09:07.900 --> 00:09:09.899
all the injustice Official Gu
has endured

00:09:09.900 --> 00:09:11.300
will be for nothing.

00:09:16.539 --> 00:09:17.499
Tell me,

00:09:17.659 --> 00:09:19.700
what exactly happened
to Lady Gu back then?

00:09:21.299 --> 00:09:22.859
Madam

00:09:23.500 --> 00:09:24.739
contracted a venereal disease.

00:09:24.900 --> 00:09:26.139
A venereal disease?

00:09:26.419 --> 00:09:27.480
Madam valued her reputation.

00:09:27.480 --> 00:09:29.420
She was known as
a refined lady of a noble family.

00:09:29.660 --> 00:09:31.319
She seldom stepped
beyond the inner quarters.

00:09:31.319 --> 00:09:32.859
No one knows how she became ill.

00:09:32.939 --> 00:09:34.859
At the time,
the rumors spread everywhere.

00:09:35.075 --> 00:09:37.139
In the end,
unable to bear the humiliation,

00:09:37.500 --> 00:09:40.019
she hanged herself
on Official Gu's birthday.

00:09:41.260 --> 00:09:43.379
To preserve the family's honor,

00:09:43.659 --> 00:09:45.339
the Duke had her cast into a mass grave,

00:09:45.340 --> 00:09:46.580
buried under another name,

00:09:46.699 --> 00:09:48.859
and forbade anyone to mention her.

00:09:51.140 --> 00:09:52.739
She never left the house.

00:09:52.740 --> 00:09:54.180
How could she have fallen ill?

00:10:01.939 --> 00:10:04.658
(So the strange illness
recorded in the family letters)

00:10:04.659 --> 00:10:05.932
(was a venereal disease.)

00:10:06.140 --> 00:10:08.420
(Could there be more to the story?)

00:10:09.659 --> 00:10:10.779
Miss Song.

00:10:26.500 --> 00:10:27.379
Mother,

00:10:27.380 --> 00:10:28.778
today is my birthday.

00:10:28.779 --> 00:10:31.060
Why will you not come celebrate with me?

00:10:32.699 --> 00:10:34.779
You are the son of the Duke's household.

00:10:35.262 --> 00:10:36.862
(Gu's Mother)
If I go,

00:10:38.260 --> 00:10:40.820
I fear I will tarnish your name.

00:10:41.699 --> 00:10:43.019
You are my mother.

00:10:43.020 --> 00:10:44.339
Who would dare speak ill of you?

00:10:44.340 --> 00:10:46.340
I would never spare them.

00:10:50.059 --> 00:10:52.207
Young Master, the celebration has begun.

00:10:53.020 --> 00:10:55.339
Ye, be good.

00:10:55.340 --> 00:10:56.660
Go now.

00:10:57.140 --> 00:10:58.418
When you return,

00:10:58.419 --> 00:11:01.540
I will cook you
a bowl of longevity noodles.

00:11:02.220 --> 00:11:04.180
All right, it is a promise.

00:11:06.340 --> 00:11:07.611
A promise.

00:11:07.612 --> 00:11:09.092
Go on, Young Master.

00:11:25.140 --> 00:11:26.340
Mother.

00:11:27.260 --> 00:11:28.619
Mother.

00:11:29.220 --> 00:11:30.859
Mother.

00:11:34.620 --> 00:11:36.259
Mother.

00:11:39.612 --> 00:11:41.607
Mother.